
==Installation==

You will need:

 http://wiki.apertium.org/wiki/Trmorph

Use the instructions on the Wiki to download and compile. To make 
tr-mor.ol, run the following in the trmorph directory:

 hfst-invert -i trmorph.a | hfst-fst2fst -O -o tr-mor.ol

You need to make a symlink from the Turkish analyser:

 ln -s /path/to/tr-mor.ol tr-ky.automorf.hfst

Now run make:

 make

And test:

 echo "Ahmet okula gitti." | apertium -d . tr-ky-bil
^Ahmet<np>/Ахмет<np><ant><m>$ ^okul<n><dat>/мектеп<n><dat>$ ^git<v><t_past><3s>/кет<v><t_past><3s>$.

